Andrew K. BONNER, Jr., Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
CUMBERLAND REGIONAL HIGH SCHOOL DISTRICT, Defendant-Respondent. C-596 September Term 2017
080173 Supreme Court of New Jersey. February 9, 2018 **161To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004133-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

**162It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
